            <title>[SPARK-2168] History Server renered page not suitable for load balancing</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SPARK-2168</link>
                <project id="12315420" key="SPARK">Spark</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Small issue but still.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I run history server through Marathon and balance it through haproxy. The problem is that links generated by HistoryPage (links to completed applications) are absolute, e.g. &amp;lt;a href=&quot;http://some-server:port/history/...&quot;&amp;gt;completedApplicationName&amp;lt;/a&amp;gt; , but instead they should be relative, e.g.  &amp;lt;a hfref=&quot;/history/...&quot;&amp;gt;completedApplicationName&amp;lt;/a&amp;gt;, so they can be load balanced. &lt;/p&gt;</description>
